                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q9",
                      "fieldName": "q9",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q22_input",
                        "name": "q9"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " is of little interest to lawyers, who are more concerned with making money. This may well be the case with some individuals, in the same way that some "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "23"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q10",
                      "fieldName": "q10",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q23_input",
                        "name": "q10"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " or scientific experts may also be driven purely by financial greed. However, criticising lawyers because their work is concerned with people's problems would be similar to attacking IT staff or "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "24"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q11",
                      "fieldName": "q11",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q24_input",
                        "name": "q11"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " for the same reason. In fact, many lawyers focus on questions relating, for example, to housing or civil liberties, which requires them to have "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "25"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q12",
                      "fieldName": "q12",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q25_input",
                        "name": "q12"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " to their work. What's more, a lot of lawyers' time is spent writing "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "26"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q13",
                      "fieldName": "q13",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q26_input",
                        "name": "q13"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " rather than dealing with people's misfortunes."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "\n                 "
                }
              ]
